'''''Star Wars Insider'' 72''' is the seventy-second issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands on [[December 2]], [[2003]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"From the Editor's Desk"
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Star News]]" {{C|by [[Lisa Stevfens]]}}
*"[[Star Sightings]]" {{C|by [[Benjamin Harper]]}}
*"[[HoloNet News (Insider)|HoloNet News]]" {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
**"[[Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 15:01:03]]"
**"[[CIS Shadowfeed Year's Start Fete Day Edition]]"
*"[[Gamescape]]" {{C|by [[W. Haden Blackman]] & Dave Gross}}
**Star Wars Galaxies Update: The Empire Expanded {{C|by [[W. Haden Blackman]]}}
**[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic|Pretty in PC]] {{C|by Dave Gross}}
*"[[Set Piece]]" &mdash; Death Star II: Emperor's Throne Room  {{C|by [[Chris Trevas]]}}
*"[[Bookshelf]]" &mdash; [[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force|A Forceful Conclusion]] {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*"[[Comics Link]]" &mdash; "Remember the Death Star!" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" &mdash; Spooky Vader, Silent Artoo, Weird Chewbacca! {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Steve Sansweet]]}}
*"[[Toy Box]]" &mdash; Convention & Clone Wars {{C|by starwars.hasbro.com}}
*"[[Crossword (department)|Crossword]]" &mdash; Special Additions {{C|by [[Michael Selinker]]}}
*"[[Star Wars Q&A|''Star Wars'' Q&A'']] {{C|by Pablo Hidalgo}}
*"[[The Last Page]]" {{C|by [[Tony Moseley]]}}

===Features===
*"[[Prequel Update]]"
*:<small>As shooting comes to a close, the action heats up, and Rick McCallum chats with the Fan Club editors on the set of Episode III.</small>
*"[[Ewan McGregor: Ready for Anything]]" {{C|by [[Gabriela Tcharner-Patao]]}}
*:<small>Ewan McGregor is quickly becoming of the biggest stars of his generation, and one of the most versatiel actors, with roles in films from ''Trainspotting'' to ''Down With Love'' to ''Star Wars Episode III''.</small>
*"[[How to Make a Star Wars Fan Film|How to Make a ''Star Wars'' Fan Film]]" {{C|by [[Mark Rusciano]]}}
*:<small>One of this year's ''Star Wars'' Fan Film Award finalists shows you how it's done.</small>
*"[[The Need for Speed: Behind the Endor Chase Scene in Return of the Jedi|The Need for Speed: Behind the Endor Chase Scene in ''Return of the Jedi'']]" {{C|by [[Ron Magid]]}}
*:<small>The action might be close to the ground, but the Endor forest chase scene rivals any space battle for its technical wizardry.</small>
*"[[Designed Simplicity: Trisha Biggar]]" {{C|by [[Francis K. Lalumière]]}}
*:<small>Trisha Biggar discusses the challenge of designing costumes for the Prequels while always keeping an eye on the classic trilogy.</small>
*"[[The 2003 Star Wars Fan Film Awards]]" {{C|by [[Dave Gross]]}}
*:<small>The finalists confide their hopes and dreams before the ceremony, and then we see the triumph of victory and the agony of defeat.</small>
*"[[Grand Master: Christopher Lee on Count Dooku and a Villainous Career]]" {{C|by [[Marcus Hearn]]}}
*:<small>Christopher Lee personifies evil in many of his roles, but never so much as when portraying the elegant but duplicitous Count Dooku.</small>

